FBIS3-58278 "drweu007_q_94007" FBIS-WEU-94-007 Document Type:Daily Report 11 Jan 1994 TURKEY Syriac Spiritual Leader Kidnapped in Sirnak TA1101111794 Ankara ANATOLIA in English 1205 GMT 11 Jan 94 TA1101111794 Ankara ANATOLIA Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Idil, Dec.10 (AA) -- The priest of a church in southeastern Turkey has been kidnapped. Melki Tok, the priest of the Ogunduk Church in Sirnak's Idil township, was kidnapped by unidentified gunmen on Sunday [9 January] when he was on his way to the church by a minibus. The gunmen dragged the priest, the spiritual leader of the region's Syriacs, to the rural area. Operations are underway to find the priest.
